{
  "stem": "24515.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I then wrote a few letters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if they had anything to do with it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The British would not permit us into the Army because-- I suppose that was very sensible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did not want to obligate themselves to make our 100,000 or whatever British citizens.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the end, they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the end-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't want to be obligated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I wrote quite a few letters along those lines.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I do not know to this date whether I had anything to do with it, or not, but I was one of the first aliens to be permitted to join the Home Guard, which was the-- do you know what the Home Guard was?",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why don't you tell me about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- the-- it was-- people who were there, either too old or too young, having too much trouble-- not too much trouble-- having [? war work ?] or something, who wanted to serve, and they would back up the regular army.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were trained somewhat militarily, and played around with guarding, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was that, anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
